            <p>
                We're available to serve you <strong>Monday through Friday, 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM</strong>. 
                During these hours, you can reach us through our website, phone, or visit us 
                in person at our office.
            </p>

            <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
                <a href="/services" style="display: inline-block; padding: 1rem 2rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 25px; font-weight: 600;">
                    Explore Our Services
                </a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
